Database schemas

Source: vignettes/schemas.Rmd
schemas.Rmd

To use comlandr, you will need permissions to access several databases. The following is a list of the databases and the tables that you will need to access. We recommend that you request read access to all tables in the schemas. However below is a list of the current tables that are used in the package.
